Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,這一路順暢也非常無聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.83,0:00:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和隊長 有事做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.02,0:00:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉大叔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.05,0:00:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉的同伴們都在幹嗎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.39,0:00:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會有人來光臨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.22,0:00:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 來得真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.25,0:00:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.71,0:00:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.36,0:01:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得練練身手了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.61,0:01:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.19,0:01:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是保護鳴人的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過至今仍無法想像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人現在在幹嗎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.38,0:01:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計在吃當地的拉麵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定相當悠閒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛田小姐 時間快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.58,0:01:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是族人的聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們日向一族在木葉中擔當著重要的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.68,0:01:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在即將開始的第四次忍界大戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為木葉的感知型忍者 將會接受很多任務
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.58,0:01:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然各自的部署不同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.64,0:01:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若事態緊急 必須有人統領一族
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.85,0:02:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已受命留守
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.67,0:02:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花火尚且年輕 實戰經驗不足
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.51,0:02:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧次 拜託你在前線替我統領一族
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.63,0:02:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分家的人 宗家明明有雛田小姐在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧次的實力大家有目共睹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 寧次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請三思而後行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些年來 雛田小姐刻苦修行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日足大人您也該有所耳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨自面對佩因的那份勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有求於我 什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…請指導我修煉柔拳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是雛田小姐是宗家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗家會由花火來繼承
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人同自來也大人一同外出修行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這期間 我也想盡可能修行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的修行也許會很嚴格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不介意的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔步.雙獅拳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得漂亮 雛田小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 她還有進步的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這並非從日向家的立場考慮 而是身為忍者而言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她無法穩住軍心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:05:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛田太過善良
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怨身為隊長的我無法執行任務
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.87,0:06:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第八班也算正式解散了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄得大家各自執行任務呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真覺得對不起你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能原諒我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是女同胞之間好溝通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是和牙或志乃就說不通咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛田啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好吧 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來很忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然剛執行完任務
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是不如綱手大人和老爸那樣忙碌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開村子了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和天天一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將補給物資送給鳴人他們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他精神著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今早天天才…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:07:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻和丁次在執行任務時也和他們偶遇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人剛才找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有任務啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.85,0:07:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅老師 我還會再來拜訪的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要和鳴人有關就會這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.71,0:07:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了…名字已經起好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.29,0:07:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡要是這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人現在應該在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這個時間在哪兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 根據日程安排 應該在暗號部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是計劃不如變化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我過去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人已經走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:08:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗號部正在編製通用於忍者聯軍的暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於比預定的時間晚 所以被訓斥了一番
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.08,0:08:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著好像是去確認糧食的儲備狀況了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.17,0:08:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人早就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.21,0:08:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 雛田 是來這幫忙的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望能再增派些人手過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.12,0:08:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食糧接二連三地進來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人知道這場戰爭將要持續多久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人說過要去確認忍具
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人已經走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天天是在執行任務時遇到鳴人的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去送補給物資的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會有其他類似的任務嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.16,0:08:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人說要去視察醫療班
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:08:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人 說是來不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我稍後向她報告一下就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都來幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是懂些醫藥知識的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是兵糧丸的負責人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.01,0:09:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天天啊 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要不要大家聚一起玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去烤肉店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉 我去我去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.79,0:09:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可沒有邀請你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說女孩子們聚一聚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦個女生聚會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先鋒部隊的第一到第五隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是根據各自的能力劃分的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇襲部隊和幾支資源補給部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會通過其他方式進行劃分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了保證木葉的忍者與其他村子的忍者平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說那麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.53,0:10:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微照顧一下上了年紀的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因你們年長我已經有所注意了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎	
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們已經經歷了兩次忍界大戰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你們能將那些經驗傳授給下一代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒白活這麼久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆還早著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戒酒戒賭的我如此認真地工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可原定的計劃還是無法順利進行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近想想 還是因為沒有同伴而感到痛心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們的時代過於殘酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你的同期夥伴都不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如此 連大蛇丸都覺得讓人懷念了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙就算健在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不可能和木葉統一戰線的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:11:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 讓您聽我說傻話了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會有我們智囊團啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾各位開會了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大名大人有事商談
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…所以計劃才總是停滯不前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛田啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有什麼任務啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 日足向我匯報
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前線統領日向一族的任務交由寧次了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那並非是輕視你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做好該做的事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持現狀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人 到時間了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是父親他…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為我的力量還遠遠不足
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.12,0:11:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒肉Q重新開業啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經預約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.54,0:12:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛舌 牛舌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新套餐 僅限女性 女生套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太划算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,划算這詞總是讓人無法抵擋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦白說 我喜歡內臟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定好飲料了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 服務員 我們要點餐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.77,0:12:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好不容易聚齊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.04,0:12:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對面是女生聚會的話 這邊就是男生聚會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡情吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大名大人跟你談什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.30,0:12:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算哪門子商談啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.01,0:12:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡說些愚蠢至極的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個怎樣 那個如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉哩巴嗦 唸唸叨叨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到這
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜音 去喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要戒酒的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我要喝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.72,0:12:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.81,0:12:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼聚會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:13:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在備戰 每天都很匆忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也要放鬆下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 偶爾這樣也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通任務都沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都在備戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話 很高興你們邀請我參加
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都是什麼關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦 為啥我們幾個總是見面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為大家一起接受中忍考試的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.85,0:13:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的是的 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是同期生啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.34,0:13:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且經常一起執行任務
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中忍考試啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢阻撓我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.57,0:13:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話 什麼忍者聯軍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子還真不容易接受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像裡脊肉 牛腰肉 心 肚腸 肝臟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.28,0:13:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都放在一個盤子裡一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,種類繁多 不是很划算嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要跟烤肉混為一談
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂就不提了 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉跟其他的村子並非一直友好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.08,0:14:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說跟雲也有過紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 不只是木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他村子間也有許多問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.24,0:14:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是哪個村子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都對其他村子有些想法倒是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.37,0:14:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 五影也決定建立忍者聯軍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來曉相當強大啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是上了戰場 一定會拚命戰鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可那時身邊如果是生人的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.09,0:14:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是怕生的類型吧 牙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.95,0:14:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦 一個一個去記也很麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們幾個聚在一起 就會想起那時的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.37,0:14:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果 那時的中忍考試終止了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摧毀木葉的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:15:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了很多事 好在沒人犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.59,0:15:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這一代相當優秀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 就佐助不在了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我多嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時 想要帶回佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果失敗了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說為什麼的話 因為沒帶上我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.18,0:15:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在怨恨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很艱苦的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家還是克服了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是一種經驗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失落者變成兩名了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有失落呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得參加中忍考試非常值
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然敗給了寧次 但雛田也很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.83,0:15:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時 他給我加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:16:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人給我加油了 我才能堅持下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 意外性是從那時開始的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會變成拯救村子的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次 輪到我們幾個保護鳴人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們幾個…來保護鳴人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還是跟那時一樣笨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.32,0:16:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個烤好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.35,0:16:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於有食慾了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要增加更多的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 五花肉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五花肉 五花肉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會變成豬的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢 都是膠原蛋白啊 膠原蛋白 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得少了誰 原來是鳴人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人在的話 就全齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.81,0:17:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在到底在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會在吃烤肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.67,0:17:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是在海上呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚 今天又是魚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.23,0:17:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也想吃烤肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝酒當然是要配肉 肉 肉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是肉跟酒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走得太快了 綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在這裡填滿肚子才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是女孩子啊 今天怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…女生聚會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生聚會嗎 讓我也參加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 綱手大人好像已經不能被稱為女生…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 是因為胸部太大了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時來份燒酒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼「暫時」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:18:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 在說自己喜歡的男生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說中忍考試的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是過去的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是這個時期啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾大家聚一下熱鬧熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛田 剛剛的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道自己該做什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個…真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 你們幾個 來賭博吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天天把綱手大人也叫來女生聚會了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太大膽了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積壓了很大壓力啊 第五代
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飽了 吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.79,0:19:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久沒吃烤肉吃得這麼香了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.39,0:19:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續啊 繼續啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去了 明天要早起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.09,0:19:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事今天必須完成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 綱手大人 今天就到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的拉麵…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可靠的傢伙們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.64,0:19:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.65,0:19:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 喝到早上…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這麼想 還是回去工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.74,0:19:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧次哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:20:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想變得更加強大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的你 已經很厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.82,0:20:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的戰爭是為了保護鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 需要更多的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.91,0:20:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為鳴人 我才會進步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.40,0:20:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟雛田小姐一樣 是他給了我自由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.45,0:20:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.41,0:20:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 子卯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該由宗家的你在戰場上統領
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:20:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在沒有宗家和分家之分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧次哥哥很適合
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.46,0:21:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如不能集結力量 是無法贏得戰爭的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.96,0:22:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濃眉老師
